              <span class="comparison-icon comparison-icon--green"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i></span>
              <div class="comparison-content">
                <h4>Automatic everything</h4>
                <p>Pricing, confirmations, notifications — handled</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="comparison-item">
              <span class="comparison-icon comparison-icon--green"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i></span>
              <div class="comparison-content">
                <h4>Orders in seconds</h4>
                <p>No typing, no calls, no back-and-forth</p>
